<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FIR Draft</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; line-height: 1.6; margin: 40px; color: #333; background: #fff; }
        .container { width: 80%; margin: auto; border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 30px; box-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        h1 { text-align: center; color: #cc0000; margin-bottom: 30px; font-size: 24px; }
        .section { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .section-title { font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px; text-decoration: underline; }
        .content { margin-left: 20px; }
        .signature-block { margin-top: 50px; text-align: right; }
        .signature-line { border-top: 1px solid #000; width: 200px; margin-left: auto; margin-top: 5px; padding-top: 5px; }
        .footer { margin-top: 50px; font-size: 12px; text-align: center; color: #666; }
        .bold { font-weight: bold; }
        .italic { font-style: italic; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>DRAFT FIRST INFORMATION REPORT (FIR)</h1>

        <div class="section">
            <p>To,</p>
            <p>The Station House Officer,</p>
            <p>Police Station {{ police_station | default('[Police Station Name]') }}</p>
            <p>Subject: Complaint regarding <span class="bold">{{ requested_action | default('[Nature of Complaint]') }}</span></p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p>Respected Sir/Madam,</p>
            <p>I, <span class="bold">{{ complainant_name | default('[Complainant Name]') }}</span>, son/daughter of {{ father_name | default('[Father\'s Name]') }}, aged {{ age | default('[Age]') }} years, residing at <span class="bold">{{ complainant_address | default('[Complainant Address]') }}</span>, bearing contact number <span class="bold">{{ phone_number | default('[Your Phone Number]') }}</span>, wish to lodge a complaint regarding the following incident:</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title">Details of Incident:</div>
            <div class="content">
                <p><span class="bold">Date of Incident:</span> {{ incident_date | default('[Incident Date]') }}</p>
                <p><span class="bold">Time of Incident:</span> {{ incident_time | default('[Incident Time]') }}</p>
                <p><span class="bold">Location of Incident:</span> {{ incident_place | default('[Place where incident occurred]') }}</p>
                <p><span class="bold">Facts of the Incident:</span></p>
                <p>{{ incident_description | default('I hereby lodge this complaint regarding the following incident: [Provide detailed description of the incident, including what happened, when it happened, who was involved, and any other relevant details. Be specific about the criminal acts committed and mention any witnesses if available.]') | replace('\n', '<br>') | safe }}</p>
                <p><span class="bold">Stolen/Damaged Items (if any):</span> {{ stolen_items | default('[Stolen Items]') }}</p>
                <p><span class="bold">Witness Details (if any):</span> {{ witness_details | default('[Witness Details]') }}</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p>I request you to kindly take necessary action and register an FIR in this regard.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <p>Thanking you,</p>
            <p>Yours faithfully,</p>
        </div>

        <div class="signature-block">
            <p>(<span class="bold">{{ complainant_name | default('[Complainant Name]') }}</span>)</p>
            <div class="signature-line"></div>
            <p>Date: {{ current_date }}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Note: This is a draft FIR. It should be submitted to the nearest police station for official registration.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
